 and the diffuse component is reproduced equally from all the loud\nspeakers after decorrelation. This scheme of spatial speech communication is\nshown to be effective and more natural for hands-free telecommunication,\nthrough either loudspeaker listening or binaural headphone listening with head\nrelated transfer function (HRTF) based presentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Sep 2021 20:16:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-13"}
