etric Toda flow on\n$\\mathcal{O}_\\lambda$. We show that it preserves positivity, and that on the\ntotally nonnegative part, it is a gradient flow in the K\\\"ahler metric up to\napplying the twist map. This extends a result of Bloch, Flaschka, and Ratiu\n(1990).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Sep 2021 20:50:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Oct 2021 23:11:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 22 Nov 2021 21:21:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-04"}
