of asymmetry is also found to increase for small-angle reconnection and\nfor more localised reconnection regions. This work shows that the curvature of\nthe coronal loops plays a role in the asymmetry of the reconnection jets and\ninward directed jets are more likely to occur and more energetic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 13:10:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
