erant -- conditions. On average, the new system achieves a\nrelative word error rate reduction of 42.18\\% compared to the audio-only model,\npointing at a high effectiveness of the proposed integration approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 14:05:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-13"}
