am of the isotropic case, we find the\nanisotropic interaction to be more advantageous for the observation of\nsupersolid phases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 14:59:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 11:03:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-31"}
